### Welcome to Null Foundry's GitHub Page.
Null Foundry is a team of developers that strive to create fun and engaging independent gaming experiences for a variety of platforms.


### Project Overview
This repository is explicitly for open-source projects and contributions by the Null Foundry team. Anyone can utilize or contribute the code found within. 


### Founders and Contributors
Anyone can contribute to our open-source projects. The Null Foundry team consists of a small group of dedicated devs. More information on our team can be found at our website www.nullfoundry.com. Other contributors to Null Foundry's work are as follows:


### Support or Contact
If you need help or guidance Dennis Bonner (@dfbonner), Etienne Magnin (@emagnin), and Michael Mitchell (@LaZZer010) are all founding members and would be glad to lend a hand. Feel free to post issues or message the team anytime.
